{"tid":1658734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岑子杰 唔係第一次遇襲！請各位注意！停止互屌！","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T05:11:19.000Z","uid":37504,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"12f058baa76ce60c732e049960886a1d06e816fb","tid":1658734,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>民陣岑子杰與友人遇襲　遭兩蒙面漢持壘球棍鐵通攻擊　友人受傷送院<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">立場報道2019/8/29 &mdash; 14:42</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n岑子杰向《立場新聞》證實，在今日中午約 12 時50分，他和數名民陣友好正在佐敦一間餐廳吃飯，<span style=\"color: red;\">期間有兩名非華裔</span>、手持壘球棍和鐵通的男子走進餐廳，並用武器敲擊餐檯。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/岑子杰與友人遭壘球棍-鐵通襲擊-友人手臂受傷-送院治理/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0%E8%88%87%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E5%A3%98%E7%90%83%E6%A3%8D-%E9%90%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86%2F&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=ad4fb683\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0%E8%88%87%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E5%A3%98%E7%90%83%E6%A3%8D-%E9%90%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%87%82%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86%2F&h=cababc26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/岑子杰與友人遭壘球棍-鐵通襲擊-友人手臂受傷-送院治理/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當日連登仔反應</span></span><br />\n<br />\n突發！岑子杰被長刀蒙面男子襲擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1515358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1515358</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意岑子杰仲清醒</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/民陣召集人岑子杰遇襲-大量流血倒地-送院時清醒/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E5%8F%AC%E9%9B%86%E4%BA%BA%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%E5%80%92%E5%9C%B0-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%99%82%E6%B8%85%E9%86%92%2F&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=c48409ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E5%8F%AC%E9%9B%86%E4%BA%BA%E5%B2%91%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%B0%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%E5%80%92%E5%9C%B0-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%99%82%E6%B8%85%E9%86%92%2F&h=4c0b0b08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/民陣召集人岑子杰遇襲-大量流血倒地-送院時清醒/</a><br />\n<br />\n請各位自行分析兩次遇襲後風向完全不同，其實岑子杰係仲清醒，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請大家先停止將遇襲關聯到和勇，裝修定唔裝修，南亞定唔南亞，甚至講到法案。請停止再拎遇襲黎帶風向，互相指責</span></span><br />\n<br />\n等岑子杰回應出黎，再自行分析<br />\n<br />\n記住：<br />\n不分和勇<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e54df9d8ab005b736672e722ef56e8650403d70d","tid":1658734,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n辛苦製作，求手足幫推！！！"},{"pid":"2b22430fd12ed16f46485b75c9a094d92f09c6a4","tid":1658734,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3b72e27f8395a357ed55f0738ca99260091c6c49","tid":1658734,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fbf02742fecd40ac11323895e301510f0d72d37","tid":1658734,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"880dcdd82a4543eae7cdceeaf864b695a7693ae7","